    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_88102">Well, how many classes can haste, Haste beyond the existing cap, increase spell damage, buff multiple stats, slow, mez, pull, increase multiple resists by 100+, debuff resists, dot, DD, snare, regen hp, regen mana, charm, DA, and mana drain?  All without mana?<br />
<br />
Bards are so powerful for 2 reasons, they have almost every utility in the game (save ports), and they have that utility without a need for mana (with exceptions on a few select songs).  To be honest, its utility thats the bane of balance in the game.  If they gave Warriors an AC/ATK debuff like a bard song (and high agro), Monks a group Regen/mana regen 'aura' like a bard song, and rogues a 50% Slow/dot ability, again like a bard song, I'm willing to bet 3 classes would stop 90% of their bitching (tho 1 would be bitching even louder).<br />
<br />
Of coarse SoE would never consider anything along those lines so we'll listen to people bitch about overpowered classes like bard, and people of those classes bitch that they are not too powerful so they dont get nerfed. Quit undressing me with your eyes<br />
&quot;Classes are not that out of balance --AbsorEQ&quot;</div>
