    <div align="left" id="post_message_88105">Quote:Well, how many classes can haste, Haste beyond the existing cap, increase spell damage, buff multiple stats, slow, mez, pull, increase multiple resists by 100+, debuff resists, dot, DD, snare, regen hp, regen mana, charm, DA, and mana drain? All without mana?<br />
<br />
And all of that is balanced by the fact that bards can only do 3 things reliably at any given time, usually only 1-2 during raids.<br />
<br />
Quote:If they gave Warriors an AC/ATK debuff like a bard song (and high agro), Monks a group Regen/mana regen 'aura' like a bard song, and rogues a 50% Slow/dot ability, again like a bard song, I'm willing to bet 3 classes would stop 90% of their bitching (tho 1 would be bitching even louder).<br />
<br />
<br />
Yes bards would bitch, because those classes would not lose any power while doing those songs. Sure, give the warriors an AC/ATK debuff song, but you can't attack with your offhand while singing it. Give monks a group regen song, but you cant Do your flying kick.<br />
<br />
Playing a bard is not like playing any other class in this game, and posts like yours only go to prove that people that have no clue are the ones bitching. Playing a bard is all about situations and choices. Group needs the bard to pull? ok, I will be oor for mana song 60% of the time while I am pulling. Want me to overhaste/haste/damage shield. Ok, I can't reliably sing mana song. Want me to add insane reisist to the whole raid? Fine, I need an instument in hand so my melee is now that of a caster.<br />
<br />
Yes bards can do all those things you just said, but bards cannot do them all at once. </div>
