    <div align="left" id="post_message_88118">The beauty of EQ is that you can play any class you want to.  You aren't born into a class.  Play whichever class you think is the most powerful, if power is what makes EQ the most fun for you.  I have several 61+ characters and find fun in all of them.  There have been certain times when one class was the most powerful, but you would be amazed at how power balance swings from class to class.  Almost everyclass has been overpowered at one point or another.   </div>
