    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_88123">It's still a problem with the Bard's invis song breaking Hide/Sneak/SoS.  I died a few times in BoT the other day while scouting just because some Bard (in my group) ran past me with that crappy invis song playing.  They passed me, their wannabe invis faded (my Hide and Sneak still active) and the giants proceeded to pummel me senseless.<br />
<br />
Ok, ok, was an accident....it happens.  I &quot;politely&quot; tell the bard to stop running around and just to stand still and do something useful like play the mana-battery song or whatever, and head over to sneak pull something...same bard runs through on their way to &quot;get another player&quot; for the group.  Wannbe invis fades, I die again.<br />
<br />
Just changing it so their silly invis song is SELF-ONLY would satisfy me.  I could care less if a bard could solo Rallos Zek or whatever the other whiners seem to think about bards being so omnipotent supposedly.  I'm just tired of dying as a result of a side-effect.<br />
<br />
